295
00:29:16,020 --> 00:29:21,856
It was as if
there were four razors...

296
00:29:21,980 --> 00:29:24,938
Cutting her at the same time...

297
00:29:25,060 --> 00:29:26,573
But invisible ones.

298
00:29:26,700 --> 00:29:32,013
