Freddy's coming for you.

307
00:30:28,180 --> 00:30:29,772
Three...four...

308
00:30:29,900 --> 00:30:33,290
Better lock your door.

309
00:30:33,420 --> 00:30:35,297
Five...six...

310
00:30:35,420 --> 00:30:38,969
Grab your crucifix.

311
