Gross.

323
00:31:51,140 --> 00:31:53,176
Help!

324
00:32:08,140 --> 00:32:09,289
Hold on, baby!

325
00:32:09,420 --> 00:32:10,773
Mom!

326
00:32:15,860 --> 00:32:16,690
I'm OK.

327
00:32:16,820 --> 00:32:19,618
-You're OK?
-I'm OK.

328
00:32:19,740 --> 00:32:22,174
But I heard you screaming.
You were calling me.

329
00:32:22,300 --> 00:32:25,610
I just slipped getting out
of the tub, Mom.

330
00:32:25,740 --> 00:32:26,934
But I told you...

331
00:32:27,060 --> 00:32:29,176
Hundreds of people a year
get killed like that, honey.

332
00:32:29,300 --> 00:32:31,131
I know, but I'm OK, Mother.

333
00:32:31,260 --> 00:32:32,818
I'm sorry for scaring you.

334
00:32:34,460 --> 00:32:36,257
I'll turn down your bed.

335
