473
00:47:01,300 --> 00:47:03,211
Thank God.

474
00:47:06,700 --> 00:47:09,168
What the hell are dreams anyway?

475
00:47:09,300 --> 00:47:10,335
Mysteries.

476
00:47:10,460 --> 00:47:12,610
Incredible body hocus-Pocus.

477
00:47:12,740 --> 00:47:15,334
The truth is we still
don't know what they are...

478
00:47:15,460 --> 00:47:17,655
Or where they come from.

479
00:47:25,380 --> 00:47:28,053
She's going into deep sleep now.

