00:47:38,900 --> 00:47:41,175
She could dream at any time now.

485
00:47:44,780 --> 00:47:46,611
Beta waves are slowing.

486
00:47:51,300 --> 00:47:53,973
She's into REMs now.

487
00:47:54,100 --> 00:47:55,818
She's definitely dreaming now.

488
00:47:55,940 --> 00:47:58,738
It's a good one, too.

489
00:47:58,860 --> 00:48:00,691
Typical dream parameter.

490
00:48:00,820 --> 00:48:05,769
A nightmare now would be
plus or minus five or six.

491
00:48:05,900 --> 00:48:08,892
She's about three.

492
00:48:15,660 --> 00:48:16,979
Doctor, what's she doing now?

493
00:48:17,100 --> 00:48:19,250
Is she asleep or awake?

494
00:48:19,380 --> 00:48:21,655
Something's wrong.
It never gets this high.

495
00:48:22,740 --> 00:48:23,775
What's she doing?

496
00:48:23,900 --> 00:48:25,128
I don't know.

497
00:48:25,260 --> 00:48:26,454
Is she dreaming?

498
00:48:34,260 --> 00:48:36,649
Nancy, it's Mom!

499
00:48:40,660 --> 00:48:41,570
What?

500
00:48:41,700 --> 00:48:42,928
Her hair.

501
00:48:43,060 --> 00:48:43,936
Ex cuse me.

502
00:48:44,060 --> 00:48:45,175
This'll help you sleep.

503
00:48:48,380 --> 00:48:49,369
Oh, my God, her arm!

504
00:48:49,500 --> 00:48:50,455
Get something.

505
00:48:50,580 --> 00:48:52,411
What happened, baby?

506
00:48:52,540 --> 00:48:53,973
What happened?

507
00:48:57,460 --> 00:48:58,813
It's OK.

508
00:49:01,380 --> 00:49:04,497
I brought something out
from my dream.

509
00:49:04,620 --> 00:49:06,417
Where did you get that?

510
00:49:08,020 --> 00:49:10,295
I grabbed it off his head.

511
00:49:24,020 --> 00:49:27,410
She said she grabbed it off
his head in her dream.

512
00:49:27,540 --> 00:49:28,973
No, I'm not crazy.

513
00:49:29,100 --> 00:49:31,568
I'm holding the damn thing
right here in my hand.

514
00:49:31,700 --> 00:49:33,850
I don't know where
she really found it.

515
00:49:33,980 --> 00:49:35,299
I gotta go.

516
00:49:46,660 --> 00:49:49,652
You didn't sleep at all
last night, did you?

517
00:49:49,780 --> 00:49:52,772
You know the doctor says
you have to sleep, or...

518
00:49:52,900 --> 00:49:54,856
