531
00:50:35,220 --> 00:50:36,539
It's real, Mama.

532
00:50:36,660 --> 00:50:38,059
Feel it.

533
00:50:38,180 --> 00:50:39,738
Give me that damn thing.

534
00:50:39,860 --> 00:50:41,691
