written in it.

535
00:50:41,820 --> 00:50:43,731
Fred Krueger, Mom.

536
00:50:46,260 --> 00:50:48,728
Do you know who that is, Mother?

537
00:50:48,860 --> 00:50:50,293
Because if you do,
you better tell me...

538
00:50:50,420 --> 00:50:51,773
Because he's after me now.

539
00:50:51,900 --> 00:50:55,336
Nancy, trust your mother
for once, please.

