01:12:25,660 --> 01:12:27,810
Then I guess those people don't
wake up to tell what happens.

807
01:13:53,860 --> 01:13:57,614
You dreamed about
the same creep I did.

808
01:13:57,740 --> 01:14:00,049
Gonna get you.

809
01:15:01,780 --> 01:15:02,974
I'm here!

810
01:16:44,980 --> 01:16:48,529
Come out and show yourself,
you bastard!

811
01:16:53,700 --> 01:16:55,019
Shit.

812
01:16:59,060 --> 01:17:00,049
Come on, Krueger!

813
01:17:00,180 --> 01:17:02,011
Follow me!

814
01:17:07,660 --> 01:17:10,458
Damn it!

815
01:17:10,580 --> 01:17:12,969
Where are you?

816
01:17:13,100 --> 01:17:15,091
Where are you, Krueger?

817
01:17:16,500 --> 01:17:19,412
I know you're here.

818
01:17:19,540 --> 01:17:22,498
Final 10 seconds.

819
01:17:22,620 --> 01:17:24,576
Nine, eight, seven, six...

820
01:17:24,700 --> 01:17:25,530
Bitch.

821
01:17:28,500 --> 01:17:29,774
I got you now!

822
01:17:58,460 --> 01:18:00,849
I'm crazy after all.

823
01:18:13,980 --> 01:18:16,016
Come on, Krueger!

824
01:18:16,140 --> 01:18:17,334
Take it down!

825
01:18:17,460 --> 01:18:18,939
Come and get me!

826
01:18:21,660 --> 01:18:22,456
Help!

827
01:18:22,580 --> 01:18:24,059
I've got him! Hey, Daddy!

828
01:18:24,180 --> 01:18:26,091
I've got him trapped!

829
01:18:26,220 --> 01:18:27,778
Help! Where are you?

830
01:18:27,900 --> 01:18:29,936
Everything's gonna be all right!

831
01:18:30,060 --> 01:18:31,652
Everything's under control!

832
01:18:31,780 --> 01:18:34,135
Get my dad, you asshole!

833
01:18:43,660 --> 01:18:44,888
Come on!

834
01:18:45,020 --> 01:18:46,453
He's in here!

835
01:18:46,580 --> 01:18:48,298
Don't let him kill me, too!

836
01:19:02,420 --> 01:19:03,773
Come on, Freddy.

837
01:19:03,900 --> 01:19:05,219
Can't you catch me?

838
01:19:07,700 --> 01:19:10,260
I'm going to split you in two.

839
01:19:19,460 --> 01:19:21,496
Daddy, help me, please!

840
01:19:21,620 --> 01:19:23,611
Maybe I better go
tell the Lieutenant.

841
01:19:33,900 --> 01:19:36,016
I'll kill you slow.

842
01:19:39,340 --> 01:19:40,739
Where are you?

843
01:20:13,820 --> 01:20:15,936
Daddy, I did it!

844
01:20:16,060 --> 01:20:17,049
Please hurry!

845
01:20:19,620 --> 01:20:21,417
Where are you?

846
01:20:24,660 --> 01:20:26,412
Parker, I need some help here!

847
01:20:26,540 --> 01:20:27,814
OK, you guys.
Come on, let's go.

848
01:20:27,940 --> 01:20:29,658
Let's go.
Al, Tim, get over here.

849
01:20:33,900 --> 01:20:35,697
Get you out.

850
01:20:35,820 --> 01:20:37,299
Open this door!

851
01:20:37,420 --> 01:20:39,297
Watch yourself. I got it.

852
01:20:39,420 --> 01:20:40,694
It's Krueger!

853
01:20:40,820 --> 01:20:42,139
Get out of the way.

854
01:20:47,540 --> 01:20:49,337
This way, guys. Come down here.

855
01:20:52,620 --> 01:20:54,292
Oh, my God.

856
01:20:54,420 --> 01:20:55,614
Nancy, what the hell
is going on?

857
01:20:55,740 --> 01:20:57,776
Parker, get up here!

858
01:20:57,900 --> 01:20:59,049
We got a fire up here, too.

859
01:20:59,180 --> 01:21:01,978
We're on our way up.

860
01:21:05,060 --> 01:21:07,096
What the hell is going on,
Nancy?

861
01:21:07,220 --> 01:21:08,938
He's after Mother!

862
01:21:21,460 --> 01:21:23,257
Watch out! He's under there!

863
01:21:49,460 --> 01:21:51,257
Now do you believe me?

864
01:21:51,380 --> 01:21:54,611
They've got the fires out
downstairs.

865
01:21:54,740 --> 01:21:56,492
Everything OK up here?

866
01:22:06,620 --> 01:22:08,338
I'm OK.

867
01:22:10,260 --> 01:22:12,376
You go downstairs.

868
01:22:12,500 --> 01:22:14,775
I'll be there in a minute.

869
01:22:19,380 --> 01:22:21,177
Lieutenant,
is everything all right?

870
01:22:21,300 --> 01:22:22,653
I don't know.

871
01:22:53,620 --> 01:22:55,850
I know you're there, Freddy.

872
01:22:59,980 --> 01:23:03,256
You think you was
gonna get away from me?

873
01:23:03,380 --> 01:23:05,655
I know you too well now,
Freddy.

874
01:23:07,540 --> 01:23:10,293
Now you die.

875
01:23:10,420 --> 01:23:13,378
It's too late, Krueger.

876
01:23:13,500 --> 01:23:16,856
I know the secret now.

877
01:23:16,980 --> 01:23:18,971
This is just a dream.

878
01:23:19,100 --> 01:23:21,216
You're not alive.

879
01:23:21,340 --> 01:23:25,652
This whole thing
is just a dream.

880
01:23:27,660 --> 01:23:29,696
I want
my mother and friends again.

881
01:23:29,820 --> 01:23:31,572
You what?

882
01:23:31,700 --> 01:23:36,820
I take back
every bit of energy I gave you.

883
01:23:36,940 --> 01:23:38,532
You're nothing.

884
01:23:41,460 --> 01:23:42,529
You're shit.

885
01:23:57,780 --> 01:24:00,089
It's bright.

886
01:24:00,220 --> 01:24:04,532
It's going to burn off soon,
or it wouldn't be so bright.

887
01:24:04,660 --> 01:24:06,139
Feeling better?

888
01:24:06,260 --> 01:24:08,490
Oh, I feel like a million bucks.

889
01:24:08,620 --> 01:24:09,655
They say you've bottomed out...

890
01:24:09,780 --> 01:24:12,294
When you can't remember
the night before.

891
01:24:12,420 --> 01:24:14,217
You know, baby,
I'm going to stop drinking.

892
01:24:14,340 --> 01:24:17,332
I just don't feel like it
any more.

893
01:24:17,460 --> 01:24:19,576
Did I keep you awake last night?

894
01:24:19,700 --> 01:24:22,214
You look a little bit peaked.

895
01:24:24,180 --> 01:24:26,648
I guess I just slept heavy.

896
01:24:28,620 --> 01:24:30,576
I'll see you.

897
01:24:30,700 --> 01:24:31,689
See you.

898
01:24:35,860 --> 01:24:37,179
Hi, everybody.

899
01:24:37,300 --> 01:24:38,449
You believe this fog?

900
01:24:38,580 --> 01:24:41,538
I believe anything is possible.

901
01:24:43,020 --> 01:24:44,214
Looking good, girl.

902
01:24:46,060 --> 01:24:47,209
What happened?

903
01:24:48,900 --> 01:24:50,413
What's going on?

904
01:24:50,540 --> 01:24:52,929
Hey, I'm not doing this.

905
01:24:53,060 --> 01:24:53,890
Let us out!

906
01:24:54,020 --> 01:24:54,850
I'm not doing this.

907
01:24:54,980 --> 01:24:56,493
What's going on with the window?

908
01:24:56,620 --> 01:24:58,292
No! Mother!

909
01:25:03,220 --> 01:25:04,175
What's going on?

910
01:25:08,020 --> 01:25:09,692
One, two...

911
01:25:09,820 --> 01:25:13,495
Freddy's coming for you.

912
01:25:17,540 --> 01:25:19,929
Three, four...

913
01:25:20,060 --> 01:25:23,530
Better lock your door.

914
01:25:23,820 --> 01:25:25,776
Five, six...

915
01:25:25,860 --> 01:25:28,579
Grab your crucifix.

916
01:25:28,700 --> 01:25:30,531
Seven, eight...

917
01:25:30,660 --> 01:25:33,493
Gonna stay up late.

918
01:25:33,620 --> 01:25:35,736
Nine, ten...

919
01:25:35,860 --> 01:25:40,012
Never sleep again.

